title: Your Feelings Aren't Hungry
itunes:title: Your Feelings Aren't Hungry
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

Are you are in fear of feeling "bad?" Many of us spend a lot of our lives running from feeling negative emotions. And then we run right to food to make us feel better. Today I share with you how your feelings want to be felt, not fed, and how to do that.
